Output a Java code segment that takes an array of numbers and returns the median value

### Response:
public static double getMedian(int[] a) 
{ 
    Arrays.sort(a); 
    int len = a.length; 
    if (len % 2 == 0) 
        return (a[(len/2)] +  
                a[(len/2)-1]) / 2; 
    else
        return a[len/2]; 
}

